This is a Telegram bot built with Python that generates secure, customizable passwords for users. It asks users a few simple questionsâ€”like length, inclusion of symbols or numbersâ€”and generates a random password accordingly.

## ğŸš€ Features

- Asks user for desired password length (minimum 8 characters)
- Option to include:
  - Symbols (e.g., !@#$%^&)
  - Numbers (e.g., 123456)
